videos.description: Auburn's Bryce Brown intercepts the inbound passes before dishing an assist to Jared Harper for the three.
videos.headline: Brown gets the steal and finds Harper for the 3-pointer

videos.description: Chris Silva hits the pull-up 3-pointer over an Ole miss defender to make it a 4 point game.
videos.headline: Silva knocks down transition 3-pointer

videos.description: Auburn's Jared Harper finds Chuma Okeke for the alley-oop to wrap up Auburn's first round win.
videos.headline: Harper connects with Okeke for soaring alley-oop
